			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">In the Rush to Decarbonize, the Shipping Industry Is Exploring Alternative Fuels</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">The shipping industry is finally embracing greener fuels, but which one, or ones, will they land on?</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/chris-baraniuk/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Chris Baraniuk</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
					<aside class="singlebydatewords singlepagecontainer">
